title: 12/30/20 – HOUR 1 – Where Did It All Go Wrong For Dwayne Haskins?
itunes:title: 12/30/20 – HOUR 1 – Where Did It All Go Wrong For Dwayne Haskins?
description:
LaVar Arrington and T.J. Houshmandzadeh fill in for Dan Patrick and break down Dwayne Haskins’ downward spiral since entering the league last season. The guys question if the former Ohio State product can salvage his career with a new franchise.
